      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "渚、何してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6333332618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、眠れない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1666665952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ううん。ちょっとだけ考えごと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4999999285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのこと……っていうか、琴乃ちゃんのことを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8999999285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "え……私のこと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.240317146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん。次の新曲で着るのはバレンタインの衣装でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9069838126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "可愛い系だと思うし、琴乃ちゃん似合うだろうな～って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3069839079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もう、冗談ばっかり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0860987901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "本当は、別のことなんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えへへ、さすがにバレちゃうか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9860990444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "……さっき、センターの話を聞いて、改めて思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4943227097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きっと今まで琴乃ちゃんは、センターとして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2859636862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "いろんなことを考えてくれてたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0514587815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一番注目される分、一番頑張らなきゃいけないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8676190614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "責任も感じるだろうし、逃げる訳にもいかないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7666665951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ファンのみんなからの期待はもちろん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4467395703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルのプレッシャーだって、物凄くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1772272754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今回みたいに、大きなお仕事が重なる中でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1368529875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "きっと手を抜かず、一人で背負ってきたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7333375851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうね、そうだったかもしれない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0177599191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今は違うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3508400392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "月ストのみんなと、すずが照らしてくれるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8844265858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私は一人じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3844265858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……ありがとう。その言葉が聞けて良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6844255685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そっかぁ。ふ～ん。すずちゃんね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8000032345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えぇ……？　な、なんで拗ねてるの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3376456181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "私、変なこと言ったかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3376456181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "別に拗ねてないも～ん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1043122847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
