      "text": "拗ねてないけど……うん。そうだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9000032345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（今は、すずちゃんもセンターとして立ってくれてる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0829746484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "（一人が大変な時は、もう一人が引っ張って、輝いて）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1000032345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（それなら、今回みたいに『二人』が大変な時は）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.4194823185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "（誰かが立たなきゃ……ううん、『私』が立ちたい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.3791039064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（私自身の強さ。私自身の道。まだ、それは）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9114913541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "（分からないけど、それでも。誰よりも輝きたい）",
      "translations": {
